eople cannot comprehend them and need someone to comment on them, nobody ca=
n capture the Truth more perfectly than Veda and Upanishad. So, what ends u=
p happening is that one focuses on a small part of the Truth captured by th=
em and explains it in the desa-kala-patra of one's times.
