 (if so, Veda and Upanishad are already there), but to write something more=
 direct and useful to one's audience. Every master may come with a mission =
and focus on that mission. Adi Shankara's primary mission was to stop the a=
dvance of Buddhism and show how tenets of Buddhism are contained in Vedanta=
.
