mmentary on "Ishavasyopanishad" (aka "Ishopanishad"). One can certainly vie=
w it as the great Shankara tying himself in knots! THAT upanishad really ch=
allenges the simplified main message Shankara chose to drive home in THAT i=
ncarnation!
=A0
